<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <p>Dear {{ user ? user.fullName : 'Customer' }},</p>

    <p>We're writing to give you an update on your Deckard inquiry #{{ inquiry.inquiryNumber }}. Your request is now actively being processed.</p>

    <p>This means we are currently working on your inquiry. We will notify you again as soon as there are further developments, such as when your inquiry is completed.</p>

    <p>You can view the details of your inquiry and its current status here: <a href="{{ viewUrl }}">View Inquiry</a><br>
    Thank you for your continued patience.</p>

    <p>Sincerely, The Deckard Team</p>
</body>
</html>
